---

## Pass 2: Presentation Strategy

### 2.1 Framework (Choose ONE)

| Framework | Structure | Best When |
|-----------|-----------|-----------|
| **Pyramid** | Recommendation → Arguments → Evidence → Action | Answer-first |
| **SCR** | Situation → Complication → Resolution → Implications | Problem-solving |
| **Transformation** | Old World → Disruption → New World → Imperatives | Before/after |
| **Countdown** | Stakes → Deadline → Readiness → Action | Urgency |
| **Evidence Cascade** | Foundation → Build → Conclusion → Action | Data-rich case |

**Selection**: [Framework] — [Why]

### 2.2 Opening Hook (Choose ONE)

| Hook | Pattern |
|------|---------|
| **Number** | Lead with striking statistic |
| **Question** | Provocative question |
| **Stakes** | Quantified risk/opportunity |
| **Shift** | "Everything changed when..." |
| **Contrast** | "While X... Y..." |

**Selection**: [Hook] — [Why]

### 2.3 Closing (Choose ONE)

| Technique | Pattern |
|-----------|---------|
| **Callback** | Return to opening |
| **Choice** | "Two paths..." |
| **Imperative** | Direct call to action |
| **Timeline** | "By [date]..." |
| **Question** | What matters most |

**Selection**: [Technique] — [Why]

---

## Pass 3: Slide Architecture

### 3.1 Slide Types

| Type | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| **Setup** | Context; orient audience |
| **Evidence** | Data supporting argument; visual-led |
| **Synthesis** | Interpret meaning; "so what" |
| **Action** | WHO does WHAT by WHEN |

### 3.2 Block Allocation

**Use target from 1.4. Merge/drop blocks to hit range.**

**Pyramid:**
| Block | Type | Slides | Flexible? |
|-------|------|--------|-----------|
| Opening | Setup | 1 | Fixed |
| Recommendation | Action | 1 | Fixed |
| Argument 1–3 | Evidence + Synthesis | 1–2 each | Merge/drop |
| Implications | Synthesis | 1–2 | Merge |
| Action | Action | 1 | Fixed |
| Close | Synthesis | 1 | Fixed |

**SCR:**
| Block | Type | Slides | Flexible? |
|-------|------|--------|-----------|
| Opening | Setup | 1 | Fixed |
| Situation | Setup | 1–2 | Condense |
| Complication | Evidence | 1–2 | Condense |
| Resolution | Evidence + Synthesis | 2–3 | Scale |
| Implications | Synthesis | 1–2 | Merge |
| Action | Action | 1 | Fixed |
| Close | Synthesis | 1 | Fixed |

**Transformation:**
| Block | Type | Slides | Flexible? |
|-------|------|--------|-----------|
| Opening | Setup | 1 | Fixed |
| Old World | Setup + Evidence | 1–2 | Condense |
| Disruption | Evidence | 1–2 | Scale |
| New World | Evidence + Synthesis | 2–3 | Scale |
| Imperatives | Action | 1 | Fixed |
| Close | Synthesis | 1 | Fixed |

**Countdown:**
| Block | Type | Slides | Flexible? |
|-------|------|--------|-----------|
| Opening | Setup | 1 | Fixed |
| Stakes | Evidence | 1 | Fixed |
| Deadline | Evidence | 1 | Fixed |
| Ready/Not Ready | Evidence | 2–4 | Scale |
| Reckoning | Synthesis | 1 | Merge |
| Action | Action | 1 | Fixed |
| Close | Synthesis | 1 | Fixed |

**Evidence Cascade:**
| Block | Type | Slides | Flexible? |
|-------|------|--------|-----------|
| Opening | Setup | 1 | Fixed |
| Foundation | Setup | 1–2 | Condense |
| Layers 1–3 | Evidence | 1–2 each | Scale/drop |
| Synthesis | Synthesis | 1 | Fixed |
| Action | Action | 1 | Fixed |
| Close | Synthesis | 1 | Fixed |

**Planned count**: [#]

