## Pass 4: Draft

### Slide Format
```
---
## Slide [#]: [Assertion Title]

**Type**: [Setup / Evidence / Synthesis / Action]

**Content**:
- [Bullet]
- [Bullet]
- [Bullet]

**Visual**: [Type: "Action Title"]

**Footnotes**: [If applicable]

**Speaker Notes**:
- [TRANSITION]: [From previous]
- [Content to deliver]
- [KEY POINT / PAUSE / OBJECTION PREEMPT as needed]
- [Bridge to next]

**GT Connection**: [How this supports governing thought]

**Source**: [Summary section/finding]
---
```

[Draft all slides]

